{% endif %}{% if "informix_cp4d" in components_to_install %}
---
# ............................................................................
# Informix parameters
# Valid licenseType values:
#   AEE - Specify this option if you purchased Advanced Enterprise Edition.
#   EE - Specify this option if you purchased Enterprise Edition.
#   WE - Specify this option if you purchased Workgroup Edition.
# ............................................................................
